uot;DONE&quot; to save the &#10;&#10;&#10; -Delte Cards: Double click on the card you want to delete, click on &quot;DELETE CARD&quot;. Now the card has been &#10;&#10;-Create SubTasks: Double click on the card in which you want to add subtasks, click on &quot;ADD TASK&quot; to create a &#10;&#10;-Change SubTask Title: Click on the title of the subtask you want to edit, change it, and click &quot;DONE&quot; to save the &#10;&#10;-Change Board Background colour: Click on &quot;COLOUR&quot; icon on the left side bar of the screen, choose the new background color and click &quot;SET&quot; to save the changes. Want to reset the background colour to our original colour? Click on &quot;RESET THE BACKGROUND COLOUR&quot; and click &quot;&#10;&#10;-Exit the Board: Click on &quot;EXIT&quot; icon on the left side bar of the &#10;&#10;-Delete Boards: To delete a specific board, first follow the previous steps to join the board you want to delete, on the bottom right corner, click on &quot;DELETE BOARD&quot; to delete the &#10;&#10;-See your tags: To see what tags have been created, click on the icon of &quot;TAGS&quot; in the top left corner. Now you see all existing tags.&#10;&#10;-Edit your tags: Simply go to the view of all tags, and click on the tag you want to delete pr change. And click &quot;SET&quot; to save the changes.&#10;&#10;-Delete your tag: Go to the edit view, steps about how to access edit view is in &quot;edit your tags&quot;, click on &quot;DELETE TAG&quot; to delete the specific tag.&#10;&#10;-Create Tags: Go to the list of tags, steps about how to access your list of tags is in &quot;see your tags&quot;. Click on &quot;CREATE TAG&quot;. enter the details and click &quot;CREATE&quot;.&#10;&#10;-Assign Tags to Cards: Go to the description of the card, by double clicking. You will see a list of tags, the tags with a Yellow/Orange title are tags that are already asssigned to the card. To add tags, single click on the tag you wish to add, to remove tags from the